      "content": "i dont think i want to \"let go of the pressure.\" i think i just want it to stop. everything. the noise, the thinking, the constant feeling of being a disappointment. it’s just too much to carry. sometimes i look at things and i think... wouldn't it just be easier if i could finally just get some real peace? like, actually stop?",
